desc: Lacy Pretties is an Estonian brand of handmade lingerie and swimwear for women. We take sustainable approach to fashion by using high-quality materials and producing no more than we need. Lacy is known for its romantic design, delicate lace and sustainable swimwear. All orders are made upon purchase.

layout.text: · when skies are deepest blue above, when rolling summer meadows shimmer, when the light air blows softly — scented by sweetest strawberries
